<h1 id="submit-and-approve-project-budget-revision">Submit and approve project budget revision</h1>


<p>This procedure provides information about revising a project budget. You can revise a project budget as many times as necessary, however you can't see the amount of an individual revision if the budget has been revised more than one time.</p>
<p>This task uses the SSI data set.</p>
<ol>
<li>Go to Project management and accounting &gt; Projects &gt; All projects.</li>
<li>In the list, find and select the desired record.</li>
<li>In the list, click the link in the selected row.</li>
<li>On the Action Pane, click Plan.</li>
<li>Click Project budget.</li>
<li>Click New revision.</li>
<li>Expand the Costs section.</li>
<li>In the Revision amount field, enter a number.</li>
<li>Click Save.</li>
<li>Click Workflow.</li>
<li>Click Submit.</li>
<li>In the Comment field, type a value.</li>
<li>Click Submit.</li>
</ol>
